        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " it is not necessary to think of the local leaders. While the epistle would naturally be handed to some of them in the first instance, it was addressed to the church; the church owned it and was held responsible for its public reading at the weekly worship.—",
